title.rendered: How to upload data to campaign?

content.rendered:
Step # 1

Login to admin panel

2

1

Open our landing page and click admin panel Button.

2

2

Add given login details into login form, opened in a new tab.

Step # 2

Create New Lead

2

1

Click Import lead button in Campaigns section form left menu.

2

2

Click Browse to upload (xls,csv or xlsx) file and choose campaign in which you want to upload data.

2

3

Select components of your lead items with given form fileds.

2

4

Hit ok to process Lead.

2

5

New Lead is Added in selected Campaign Successfully!.
